  Rat: {traits:"Quick-witted, resourceful, and adaptable. The Rat is the first animal — a natural pioneer who survives through intelligence, charm, and sheer hustle. You notice opportunities others miss and move on them before anyone else does.", strengths:"Clever, ambitious, sociable, detail-oriented", challenges:"Can be manipulative, restless, or overly calculating", compatible:"Dragon, Monkey, Ox", incompatible:"Horse, Goat", lucky:"2, 3 · Blue, Gold, Green", career:"Entrepreneur, writer, detective, financial analyst, politician"},
